# 1. Global Default Configuration Block (Applies to all root C files)
BasedOnStyle: WebKit
SortIncludes: false
UseTab: Always
TabWidth: 4
IndentWidth: 4
ColumnLimit: 100
BreakBeforeBraces: Attach
SpaceAfterCStyleCast: true
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align

---
# 2. Sub-Language Target Rule (Forces .glsl files to parse using the C++ parser)
Language: Cpp
